OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fnight with rain spreading eastwards
OL,7,Fand becoming heavy at times. Rain
OL,8,Fclearing western areas by morning.
OL,9,FWinds becoming strong with coastal
OL,10,Fgales before easing later in the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FHeavy rain clearing east in
OL,13,Fthe morning leaving a largely dry day
OL,14,Fwith bright spells and showers in
OL,15,Fevening. Strong winds around west
OL,16,Fcoast with winds strengthening
OL,17,Felsewhere later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
