OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain on Sunday. Sunny
OL,7,Fspells on Monday with scattered
OL,8,Fshowers. Dry with sunny spells
OL,9,FTuesday. Winds will be strong with
OL,10,Frisk of gales Sunday, then becoming
OL,11,Flight.
